  "description": "Face re(seal)",
  "body_html": "<p>The CDC says that <a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/ppe/respirators/elastomeric.html#:~:text=Elastomeric%20respirators%20protect%20against%20gases,classes%20as%20filtering%20facepiece%20respirators.\">Elastomeric respirators</a> can offer the same, or greater, level of protection than N95 FFRs in filtering out airborne particles; if used correctly. Elastomeric respirators are the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elastomeric_respirator\">reusable masks</a> that seal the face with rubber or other material. They would be useful to have in a pandemic or public health emergency, so I got one!</p><p>I\u2019m London based. So, I went to my local DIY store\u2026 (<em>this is not an ad for Screwfix btw</em>)</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!_ch5!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5b60c176-c2b4-48f8-aff9-ffdf08f9a2ef_1600x1200.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!_ch5!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5b60c176-c2b4-48f8-aff9-ffdf08f9a2ef_1600x1200.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!_ch5!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5b60c176-c2b4-48f8-aff9-ffdf08f9a2ef_1600x1200.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!_ch5!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5b60c176-c2b4-48f8-aff9-ffdf08f9a2ef_1600x1200.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!_ch5!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-